According to my education I am a philologist and a specialist in languages and communication. During my university experience I improved my creative and analytical writing skills, communicative competence in different languages and expressing in an academic style. I am always content if I have the chance to improve my communicative and writing competence and I think that I can give a lot from myself in this field. I am fluent in Bulgarian, English, Italian and Romanian. 


But the thing that I love to do the most is drawing. Apart from loving to do dedicate time to art, I also have some professional experience in this area: I was part of the organization of a few exhibitions in my home country and of one solo exhibition in Amsterdam. Also, I was a volunteer at Rijksakademie Open Studios 2019, Amsterdam. I want to experience more of the ways of creating cultural and art events and to be closer to the art societies. I am motivated to participate in different art projects and to improve more and more my art skills.
